{"tid":804641,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔子跳兔子舞 (binky) 🐰🌟🌟","createTime":"2018-09-03T07:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T07:20:06.000Z","uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"085241d02fa1e7c2e9259a3b51c468d1e17e0696","tid":804641,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"兔子binky(跳兔子舞)是兔子最開心的狀態。當牠們binky 時，這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqOeRBSpaCs&d=2udh5xhCYt10QHcWxQFnE%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=471d13da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><em>N.B.</em></span>: 實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會參觀然後領養，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=2udh5xhCYt10QHcWxQFnE%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b8ea31c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a>"}]}